<title>HONG KONG: Peregrine sets call warrants on Hopewell.</title>
<headline>Peregrine sets call warrants on Hopewell.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1996-11-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Peregrine Derivatives Ltd is issuing 424.8 million American-style call warrants on shares of Hopewell Holdings Ltd, a Peregrine official said on Monday.</p>
<p>Ten warrants control one share.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE	HK$4.635     PREMIUM	 13.8 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE	 HK$0.1228    GEARING	 4.2X</p>
<p> EXPIRATION	  28.NOV.97    MIN EXER LOT  10,000</p>
<p> LISTING	     HONG KONG    PAYDATE	 2 WKS AFTER LAUNCH</p>
<p> SPOT PRICE	  HK$5.15</p>
<p> NOTE		  GOVERNING LAW IS HONG KONG</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong Newsroom (852) 2843 6370</p>
